	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			OK, Cured silk becomes trivial at a tailoring skill of 82 and sells for about 2pp per AC                      since it is so hard to come by. The Heady Kiola is a brewers drink that is trivial to a brewer at skill 46. They sell for about 4 - 5 gp per usually and take 2 kiola saps + water + bottle. Cured silk is made in a LARGE sewing kit and you use the following combos:<BR>
<BR>
silk swatch = 2 spider silks combined in a sewing kit<BR>
<BR>
Cured Silk Sash - 1 silk swatch + belt pattern + 2 kiolas<BR>
Cured Silk Collar - 1 silk swatch + gorget pattern + 2 kiolas<BR>
Cured Silk Mask - 1 silk swatch + mask pattern + 1 kiola<BR>
Cured Silk Robe - 3 silk swatches + tunic pattern + 2 kiolas<BR>
Cured Silk Bracers - 1 silk swatch + wrist pattern + 2 kiolas<BR>
Cured Silk Sleeves - 2 silk swatches + sleeve pattern + 2 kiolas<BR>
Cured Silk Cloak - 2 silk swatches + cloak pattern + 2 kiolas<BR>
Cured Silk Headband - 2 silk swatches + cap pattern + 2 kiolas<BR>
Cured Silk Leggings - 2 silk swatches + pants pattern + 3 kiolas<BR>
Cured Silk Sandals - 1 silk swatch + boot pattern + 2 kiolas<BR>
Cured Silk Handwraps - 2 silk swatches + glove pattern + 2 kiolas<BR>
<BR>
Hope this answers your questions.<BR>
<BR>
Brilend<BR>
Nameless server<BR>
Master Fletcher<BR>
Tailor<BR>
Brewer<BR>
Blacksmith 
